Packaging Infrastruture Overview
================================
Run:
  cd package/; make

Frequently Asked Question
=========================
1. How do I build srpm?
 Run `make srpm`

2. How do I build binary package without srpm?
 Run `make rpms`

3. How do I build .el6 srpm/rpms/..?
 Run `make DIST=.el6.ucloud $(target)`
 (DIST default to be ".el7.ucloud")

4. How do I release official build as I'm the maintainer?
 Run `make release && make release-tag` and then push the changes
 In build server, pull the latest commits and run `make all-rpms`
